display_long_description:
# Come Fly With Us!

Pilot Alex the Squirrel’s plane as enemies swarm right in your space.

Dodge, shoot, and strategize.
Fast, fun, and full of chaos — **Welcome to Alex and the Jets.**

# Fly in your own surrounding
✈️ Experience your space as never before!

[media]

# Turn your surroundings into a thrilling dogfight arena.
🔫 Fight AWESOME and challenging enemies

[media]

# Use the doughnuts to gain power-ups
🍩 From poison, through shield to missile: douhgnuts will gear you up to to make sure you got what it takes

[media]

# Enjoy side-quest!
🎃 Play with bouncing pumpkins, hovering cheese and more.
